
Methodist Mmayewa Ntoaso Sukuu (Meghis) yɛ Ghana mmaayewa ntoasoɔ a ɛwɔ Mamfe, a ɛwɔ Akuapim Atifi mpesuaso wɔ Apue mantem mu.

Mamfe Methodist mmayewa dii nkunim wɔ  afe 2019 akansie a wato din World ROBOFEST a ɛkɔɔ  so wɔ  Michigan wɔ  America abrokyire man mu.

== Abakɔsɛm ==
Sukuu no hyɛɛ  ase wɔ afe 1984 sɛ  ankorakora sukuu a na wɔfrɛ  no Mamfe State College. Nanso, esan sikasem, adwumamu nhyehyɛe ne adwumayɛfoc nsemsɛm nti, wɔdanee sukuu no hyɛɛ Methodist Ghana asɔre no nsa wɔ afe 1998, ne saa nti wɔsesaa edin no kɔɔ  Methodist Ntoaso sukuu. ɛbɛdanee aban sukuu wɔ ɔpepɔn bosome, afe 1993 mu.

